              THRU S3100-DJL409C-CALL-EXT
           .
       S3000-PROCESS-EXT.
           EXIT.
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *@   DC호출
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S3100-DJL409C-CALL-RTN.

      *@3.1.1 입력파라미터 조립
      *@처리내용:처리DC입력파라미터=
      *@SET(처리구분,고객구분,차주번호,신청번호,한도신청구분)

      *    처리구분
           MOVE YNJL409C-PRCSS-DSTIC
             TO XDJL409C-I-PRCSS-DSTIC

      *    고객구분
           MOVE YNJL409C-CUST-DSTIC
             TO XDJL409C-I-CUST-DSTIC

      *    차주번호
           MOVE YNJL409C-KB-PIN
             TO XDJL409C-I-KB-PIN

      *    신청번호
           MOVE YNJL409C-APLCN-NO
             TO XDJL409C-I-APLCN-NO

      *    한도신청구분
           MOVE YNJL409C-LIMT-APLCN-DSTIC
             TO XDJL409C-I-LIMT-APLCN-DSTIC

      *@3.1.2 프로그램 호출
      *@처리내용:DC프로그램호출
           #DYCALL DJL409C YCCOMMON-CA XDJL409C-CA

      *@3.1.3 처리결과CHECK
      *@실행조건:COND-XDJL409C-OK
      *@처리내용:리턴코드가 정상(00) 아닐경우 오류처리한다
           IF COND-XDJL409C-OK
              CONTINUE
           ELSE
              #ERROR XDJL409C-R-ERRCD
                     XDJL409C-R-TREAT-CD
                     XDJL409C-R-STAT
           END-IF
           .
       S3100-DJL409C-CALL-EXT.
           EXIT.
